# PansaWatch CODEOWNERS
#
# Maps repository paths to their owning AI agent session.
# Currently advisory only (no human reviewers); reviewer assignment is
# handled by the PM Orchestrator session reading PR labels (auto-applied
# by .github/workflows/labeler.yml using .github/labeler.yml).
#
# When real human collaborators join, replace `# agent:foo` placeholders
# with `@username` to enable GitHub's automatic review request.
#
# Reference: docs/session-prompts/README.md (file matrix)

# === UI / Frontend (agent:ui) ============================================
# /components/                                # agent:ui
# /app/**/page.tsx                            # agent:ui
# /app/layout.tsx                             # agent:ui
# /app/not-found.tsx                          # agent:ui
# /app/globals.css                            # agent:ui
# /app/**/loading.tsx                         # agent:ui
# /app/**/error.tsx                           # agent:ui

